messages.text: What are you talking about??!! Are you ok?!?
What do you mean?!? What’s going on?!?
I know! Why do you need me to call the cops?!
At least that’s what I think is going on
There are men with guns out there…
I was just walking around, about to head home, got the stuff I needed…
Then the lights cut. There were screams
I stood there for a sec
Then this woman came crawling around the corner…
She kept saying over and over… Help me. Help me.
I just ran into the next store
Like a coward…Ran away from her
I’m scared to get on the phone
Don’t do anything that will give you away.
The store clerk and I are together, behind the counter
Every now and then I’ll hear shouting
Comes from close and distant place
How many are there?! Do you know??
Not sure. Sounds like a lot more then you would expect
I DON’T KNOW! Im just trying to survive
Sorry. Sorry. That was a stupid question, I know.
No, im sorry, I shouldn’t have snapped
So you want me to call the police??
Not in our store, but closer then I want
I told you not to go so late! I told you to go earlier in the day!
Like I would’ve known people were planning a robbery
If you just would’ve gone when I told you, we would be together watching it on the news!!
Well, I cant help that now can i
You hope ill die here huh?
You think that’s what I want?!
Leave me and the kids and everything???
What the hell am I thinking?! Saying that stuff.
I just wanna make it home
I love you too. So so much.
If I make it out of this alive. I’m gonna change I promise
You are. You’re going to make it out of this alive.
See your kids again. Me again.
Get back to the old times
He has a big gash on his forehead
rambling on and on, pointing at the door
causing a lot of noise, trying to quiet him
Do you want me to call someone?!?!
Store clerk has hit the silent alarm
People should be here any minute
I’ll turn on the news, see if I can get anything from there. See if they’re covering it.
In fact I see flashing lights outside
The news has picked up on it!!
Wow! Multiple vehicles surrounding that place
SWAT team is on its way
Anything I can use/need to know
They say there are at least 20-30 guys with weapons in there.
Oh god, I don’t wanna be alone!
and this idiot wont shut up
The voice is saying come out
says he wont kill us if we come out
With this blubbering idiot, we might get caught
That’s what the news just said.
do you wanna see your husband again
wat you gonna do sweet thang
do you wanna see him again
give bank account info, everything you have
Okay, okay I’ll give you whatever I want, just don’t kill him!!
The SWAT team. Saved me. Most of us!
